{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish all taxpayer-funded expenses for government employees",
        "additional_details": "Some hardworking people across the UK have to cover all work-related costs from their wages, and we do not believe government employees should be any different. We think taxpayer-funded expenses create unfair privileges and waste public money. We believe scrapping them could ensure fairness, accountability, and trust in leadership.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to abolish all taxpayer-funded expenses for government employees. We believe their wages should be used to cover all work-related costs. We believe this could ensure fairness, transparency, and responsible use of public funds, and set an example for financial accountability.",
